'''impresionism'''
#(''art'') a [[movement]] in [[art]] characterized by [[visible]] [[brush]] [[stroke]]s, [[ordinary]] [[subject]] [[matter]]s, and an [[emphasis]] on [[light]] and its changing [[qualities]]
#{{music}} a [[style]] that avoided [[traditional]] [[harmony]], and sought to invoke the [[impression]]s of the [[composer]]
#(''poetry'') a style that used [[imagery]] and [[symbolism]] to portray the [[poet]]'s impressions

